üéì Key Takeaways: Building AI Agents That Drive Value

1

Go Beyond Simple Chatbots

Measure time saved, costs reduced, revenue protected. Use concrete metrics to justify AI investment and measure ROI.

Impact: $2.9M annual savings demonstrated
4

Start with High-Pain, High-Volume Problems

Target processes that are: slow, inconsistent, expensive, or frustrating. Root cause analysis and churn prevention show immediate value.

5

Build in Layers: Reactive ‚Üí Proactive ‚Üí Predictive

Start simple (RAG + generation), add proactive monitoring (health scores), finish with predictive intelligence (churn risk, ticket storms).

Impact: Each layer multiplies value
6

Use Accessible Technology

OpenAI API, embeddings, vector search - all readily available. You don't need custom ML models to deliver business value with AI.

Impact: Build in weeks, not years
